  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">The Bottom Line</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      Engagement features have become essential differentiators in the LMS market. Enterprise platforms (Docebo, Absorb, TalentLMS) lead on gamification and structured engagement. Thinkific offers the most flexibility for experts through its app marketplace, while Kajabi excels at combining courses and communities. The key is matching engagement mechanics to your audience — competitive sales teams respond to leaderboards and points, while professional learners may prefer progress tracking and peer discussion. Whatever platform you choose, prioritize engagement features that support learning outcomes rather than distractions that feel gimmicky.
    </p>
  </section>

